      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what do you mean by \"goblin's gold\"? i thought you were saying this was a scientific explanation. can you just stick to the chemistry part? i need to know about the specific intermediate compounds that form before the final browning happens.",
      "source": "evaluator"
